@Time Duration:	10:30-11:00
@Situation:	Both Sarah and her mother have just woken up. Mother reports that last last week-end Sarah got into her mother's pocketbook and started to eat phenobarbitol pills. She was rushed to the hospital , had to stay stay overnight , and "is just now getting back to normal". During the the transcription Sarah sits at the kitchen table. The volume level of the tape is too low until near the end , probably because both Sarah and Mother are still sleepy
